    </insight>
  
  <convention>
      <p>This section <xref ref="sec-quadratic-equations-in-real-life" text="title"/> is adapted from "<url href="https://github.com/openstax/osbooks-prealgebra-bundle/tree/7fcdabf0364f3b308c0190557dfc961b579b374c/modules/m81403/index.cnxml">Solve Applications Modeled by Quadratic Equations</url>" in Open STAX Elementary Algebra 2e, used under <url href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/deed.en">CC-BY-4.0</url>.</p>
    </convention>

  <!-- END BORROWED CONTENT -->
</section>
